0x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_duranduran_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_duranduran_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_duranduran_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_duranduran_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/duran-duran">杜兰·杜兰</a>向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-lynch">大卫·林奇</a>表示敬意，称他为“富有创造力的超级英雄”和“巨大的灵感”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/david-lynch-obituary-twin-peaks-3829834">大卫·林奇 – 1946-2025：重塑电影的真正梦想家</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位资深导演和<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/twin-peaks"><em>《双峰》的</em></a>创作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">于昨天（1 月 16 日）由他的家人宣布</a>去世，据报道，他因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-reportedly-died-after-being-forced-to-relocate-from-his-house-due-to-la-wildfires-3829793">洛杉矶山火</a>“被迫搬离家”。他78岁了。</p><p>许多艺术家和导演都对他的去世表示哀悼，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steven-spielberg">史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edgar-wright">埃德加·赖特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gunn">詹姆斯·古恩</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-jackman">休·杰克曼</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">比利·科根</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/questlove">奎斯特洛夫</a>等 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">点击此处查看更多悼念</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lykke-li">Lykke Li</a>还说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lykke-li-on-how-meeting-david-lynch-changed-my-life-3829872">他“改变了我的生活”</a> 。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-are-remembering-david-lynch-through-his-favourite-bands-and-songs-3829821">林奇最喜欢的艺人之一</a>杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 在社交媒体上向键盘手尼克·罗兹 (Nick Rhodes) 表示敬意，他写道：“从我十几岁第一次看到他的电影<em>《橡皮头》</em>的那一刻起，大卫·林奇对我来说就是一位富有创造力的超级英雄。他的想象力、创新、风格和幽默仍将是巨大的灵感来源。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE6JyXWpf1C/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,